{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/f5/c8/3008_crt_ftTsK.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/f5/c8/3008_crt_ftTsK.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/f5/c8/3008_crt_ftTsK.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/f5/c8/3008_crt_ftTsK.jpg"},"name":"公安9課","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":4,"id":3008},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/95/8d/20336_crt_W9WRJ.jpg?r=1372170925","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/95/8d/20336_crt_W9WRJ.jpg?r=1372170925","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/95/8d/20336_crt_W9WRJ.jpg?r=1372170925","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/95/8d/20336_crt_W9WRJ.jpg?r=1372170925"},"name":"ロジコマ","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":20336},{"images":{"small":"","grid":"","large":"","medium":""},"name":"藤本修","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/ec/be/35866_prsn_5zZ7T.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/ec/be/35866_prsn_5zZ7T.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/ec/be/35866_prsn_5zZ7T.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/ec/be/35866_prsn_5zZ7T.jpg"},"name":"NAOTO","short_summary":"NAOTO（1983年8月30日－），本名片冈直人，是日本的舞者、演员；是男子歌舞团体EXILE的表演者、男子歌舞团体三代目 J SOUL BROTHERS的队长兼表演者。","career":["artist","actor"],"id":35866,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":73130}],"detail":[{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"male","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"","grid":"","large":"","medium":""},"summary":"","name":"藤本修","infobox":[{"key":"别名","value":[]},{"key":"性别","value":"男"}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":73130,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/f5/c8/3008_crt_ftTsK.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/f5/c8/3008_crt_ftTsK.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/f5/c8/3008_crt_ftTsK.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/f5/c8/3008_crt_ftTsK.jpg"},"summary":"由前军官、法医科学家和警察侦探组成的信息安全和情报部门。\r\n组织结构以德国GSG-9特种部队为基础，与英国特种空勤团亦有交叉训练。\r\n是直属日本内务省，听命于总局长和日本首相的独立部队。\r\n有关第9课的大部分信息为高度机密，内务省不对其活动细节发表评论。\r\n公众并不知晓第9课的存在，国会和其他安全部队部门对9课的认识也仅为一个“黑色行动单位”。这使得9课能够独立运作，不受政府监督，以避免繁文缛节和官僚主义。\r\n9课负责众多独特职能，包括国家层面的信息安全、要员保护、调查贪污、打击恐怖组织乃至于暗杀，其形态的特殊也令其直面新型犯罪事件。","name":"公安9課","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"公安9课"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"攻壳机动队"},{"v":"9课"},{"k":"英文名","v":"Public Security Section 9"},{"k":"日文名","v":"公安9課"},{"k":"罗马字","v":"Koan Kyuka"}]}],"stat":{"comments":7,"collects":77},"id":3008,"locked":false,"type":4,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/95/8d/20336_crt_W9WRJ.jpg?r=1372170925","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/95/8d/20336_crt_W9WRJ.jpg?r=1372170925","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/95/8d/20336_crt_W9WRJ.jpg?r=1372170925","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/95/8d/20336_crt_W9WRJ.jpg?r=1372170925"},"summary":"２０２２年に製造され、コンテナ内部に武器や弾薬などを収容する熱光学迷彩装備の歩兵兵站用輸送支援車両である。ロジスティクス・コンベイヤー・マシンの略称でもある。型番はＬＣＭ２２。指揮官を識別し自律支援する程度の発展型の人工知能は持ち合わせている。公安９課に試験配属されており、搭乗スペースは未搭載。装備拡張が許可され腕部パーツの取付が行われる。","name":"ロジコマ","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"逻辑克马"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"k":"英文名","v":"Rojicoma"},{"k":"日文名","v":"ロジコマ"}]}],"stat":{"comments":5,"collects":9},"id":20336,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false}]}